data.description:
Join us for the Sioux Center Dream Big Dinner at the Fruited Plain in Sioux Center to learn about the big, structural change that Elizabeth is fighting for in Iowa, and how you can be a part of our campaign.

Our team knows that to create real change – to rebuild the middle class and save our democracy – we need to dream big and fight hard. That's why we’re in this fight: to have real conversations about how to level the playing field for working families, and who is best to lead that fight.

We’ll see you there!

If you need ADA accommodations, please let our team know when you arrive.

data.description:
Elizabeth Warren is returning to Nevada! She will be hosting an organizing event in Las Vegas on Saturday, April 27 as we build our movement for 2020.

Doors open for the event at 5:00 PM and the event will begin at 6:00 PM. This event is free and open to the public, so feel free to bring your friends and family along too. Tickets aren’t required, but an RSVP is strongly encouraged. Admission will be first come, first served.

If you need ADA accommodations at this event, please let a volunteer or a member of our team know when you arrive. You can also reach out in advance at info@elizabethwarren.com. 

Thanks, and we hope to see you in Las Vegas!
data.title: Las Vegas Organizing Event with Elizabeth Warren
